I tried to make PoH but this real life work thing didn't allow me to log on until way after the raids started until after the 5th day when everybody was rather sick of PoH.<br>
<br>
For now I'm just trying to make a bit of cash so I can afford to head up there again. From what I remember LPR and Meann spent a moderately insane amount of cash with minimal return on investment. I'd like to help get some of that cash back to those that forked out the money.<br>
<br>
I've been reading on another message board that the crown drops are more random than they once were. One post on magecompendium claimed 3 crown drops in 1 clearing off island 7.<br>
<br>
On the last day we actually did anything on Island 7 Zaboxten, Slioch and myself did some pathing testing with pets. The results were fairly interesting we can probably have an easier time pulling the mobs if we apply what we learned from the tests.<br>
