<br>
Something I've talked to some people about concerning epic pieces is to find a guild that either still does or use to raid PoA regularly. A lot of them have a guild mule with a lot of nice items, possibly a crown.<br>
<br>
If you have the cash and the guild has an extra crown they might be willing to sell it to you. One thing to be forwarned about though is the price you might be asked to pay. Recently I was talking to a former guild member that joined a different guild. I found out they had extra crowns so I sent a tell to the appropriate people and was told &quot;Sure, we'll sell you a crown for 150k&quot;. If you're willing to pay that you'll have a good shot at your epic. For me however, I'm just gonna bide my time and continue to test my patience. <p>-Tweelis Twitchydigits<br>
